  "detailed_description": "<strong>\"A game where you can relax and fishing\"</strong><br><br>Need something to relax after a busy day? Want to play a game but don't want to think much? Want to play a wholesome game but only for fishing?<br><strong><i>Cozy Fishing</i></strong> is here for you. In this game, you don't need to think about managing yourself.<br>Just relax and keep fishing. Catch all the fish and fill up your <strong>Aquarium!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><strong>\"Fish in different biomes\"</strong><br>In <strong><i>Cozy Fishing</i></strong> you can fish in 4 different locations, <strong>Lake</strong>, <strong>River</strong>, <strong>Ocean</strong>, and <strong>Deep Ocean</strong>. Each biome has its <strong>unique fish species</strong> and you can visit each biome without any restriction.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567230/extras/d44c702f4afb924a9af7f2e393553873.avif?t=1702123317\" width=610 height=685 /></span>",
